    <h1>Freshness</h1>
    <p class="description">A Google ranking signal that favors recently published or updated content. Powered by the <strong>Query Deserves Freshness (QDF)</strong> algorithm — most powerful for news, trending topics, and queries with rapidly changing answers.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
